ia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Thepunching powerof Khelif saw her record a lightning-quick win over the Italian, which in turn piled more pressure on the IOC for allowing them to box in Paris.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 625, \"end\": 632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9978127269515753, \"rank\": 0.001811993138662727, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 675, \"end\": 678, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1593532367575935e-21, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999976321305, \"rank\": 2.3677859406885744e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Both fighters had been disqualified at the 2023 World Championships after failing International Boxing Association eligibility rules that prevent athletes with male XY chromosomes from competing in women's events.\", \"from\": 715, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 797, \"end\": 829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.02620888316736e-26, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 880, \"end\": 894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"XY chromosomes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the IBA was stripped of its recognition by the IOC last year over governance and finance issues, with the Olympic body running theboxingcompetition in Paris.\", \"from\": 930, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9689920479899228, \"rank\": 0.031818293804648505, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1593532367575935e-21, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1085, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999976321305, \"rank\": 2.3677859406885744e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC said the IBA decision to disqualify the boxers last year was arbitrary and the main cause for the furore that has the likes of J. K. Rowling and billionaire Elon Musk voice their opposition to them competing in the Games.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1097, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1593532367575935e-21, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1110, \"end\": 1113, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9689920479899228, \"rank\": 0.031818293804648505, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1231, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Kirkpatrick\", \"score\": 0.8486183510015959, \"rank\": 0.11493599672182256, \"text\": \"K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Kirkpatrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ralph_Kirkpatrick\"}, {\"begin\": 1258, \"end\": 1267, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'These two athletes were the victims of a sudden and arbitrary decision by the IBA,' the IOC said in a statement.\", \"from\": 1324, \"to\": 1437, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9689920479899228, \"rank\": 0.031818293804648505, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1593532367575935e-21, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Towards the end of the IBA World Championships in 2023, they were suddenly disqualified without any due process.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'According to the IBA minutes available on their website, this decision was initially taken solely by the IBA Secretary General and CEO.'\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9689920479899228, \"rank\": 0.031818293804648505, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1659, \"end\": 1662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9689920479899228, \"rank\": 0.031818293804648505, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some sports have limited the levels of testosterone allowed for athletes competing in women's competition, while others ban everyone who has been through male puberty.\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Differences of Sexual Development are a group of rare conditions involving genes, hormones and reproductive organs.\", \"from\": 1861, \"to\": 1976, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some people with DSDs are raised as female but have XY sex chromosomes and blood testosterone levels in the male range.\", \"from\": 1977, \"to\": 2096, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2029, \"end\": 2031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.999999499896046, \"rank\": 5.001042799372724e-07, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC said the rules of eligibility were based on those of the Tokyo Games in 2021 and cannot be changed during a competition.\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2102, \"end\": 2105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1593532367575935e-21, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The current aggression against these two athletes is based entirely on this arbitrary decision, which was taken without any proper procedure, especially considering that these athletes had been competing in top-level competition for many years,' the IOC said.\", \"from\": 2228, \"to\": 2488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2479, \"end\": 2482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1593532367575935e-21, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The IOC is saddened by the abuse that the two athletes are currently receiving,' it added.\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2495, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1593532367575935e-21, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Every person has the right to practice sport without discrimination.'\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tbrowser thatsupports HTML5 \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tvideo  Up Next  In a statement, the IBA condemned 'inconsistencies in eligibility' at the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2687, \"end\": 2697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.682035486101461e-14, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 2759, \"end\": 2764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 0.9999999999542979, \"rank\": 4.57262460892991e-11, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}, {\"begin\": 2809, \"end\": 2812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9689920479899228, \"rank\": 0.031818293804648505, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Both Imane Khelif and Lin Yu-ting post testing, did not meet the required eligibility criteria to compete within the female category of our respective events,' the body added.\", \"from\": 2877, \"to\": 3053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2883, \"end\": 2895, \"title\":